description:
🦀 Rust Bristol is now a thing, and we're kicking off this group with not one but 2 events and this is the first.

Program of that evening (order may change):

1. Welcome note & introduction to " 🦀 Rust Bristol"
2. Intro to Rust for programmers - *Joshua Barretto*
3. Using `std` in embedded Rust - *Tim Hutt*
4. Pioneering Autonomous Guidance Systems for the Next Generation of Aircraft - *[Volant Autonomy](https://volantautonomy.com/) (sponsor)*

Venue:
Framework
35 King Street
Bristol, BS1 4DZ
title: Rust Bristol 🦀 Kickoff (1/2) - Intro & Embedded
